These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: family, documentary, epic, sports, disaster, drama, zombie
There are 7 different favourite beverages: lemonade, almond-milk, 7up, water, soy-milk, milk, coffee
 1. the person watching family movies is between the person watching sports movies and the person watching zombie movies##2
 2. the person watching documentary movies is in the middle##1
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 4. the person watching disaster movies is between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking soy-milk##2
 5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
 7. the person drinking lemonade is between the person drinking water and the person drinking 7up##2
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
10. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
11. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | family | zombie | documentary    | epic | disaster   | drama    |
| Beverage         | milk  | almond-milk   | water | lemonade | 7up   | coffee | soy-milk |

