.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: sunflower, amaryllis, daffodil, zinnia, marigold, begonia, bellflower
There are 7 different favourite colors: light-blue, blue, ebony, red, turquise, mauve, amber
1. the person who likes mauve is on the far left##1
2. the person who growsdaffodil is between the person who growsbegonia and the person who likes mauve##2
3. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
4. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
5. the person who growsamaryllis is in the middle##1
6. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
7. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
8. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who likes red##1
9. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Flower          | marigold | daffodil | begonia | amaryllis | bellflower | sunflower      | zinnia  |
| Color   | mauve | red  | amber     | ebony     | turquise  | light-blue | blue |

