.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: superhero, thriller, animation, western, adventure, satire, musical
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, baccarat, prince, bolivar, aristoff, siglo, tiparillo
 1. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 2. the prince-smoker is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
 3. the aristoff-smoker is the person watching musical movies##1
 4. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
 5. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
 6. the person watching western movies is the bolivar-smoker##1
 7. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
 8. the pall-mall-smoker is between the tiparillo-smoker and the person watching western movies##2
 9. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
10. the person watching thriller movies is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | adventure | superhero | thriller   | western | animation | satire |
| Cigar           | aristoff | siglo     | baccarat     | prince | bolivar   | pall-mall   | tiparillo    |

