.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: trance, metal, jazz, d&b, classical, disco, r&b
There 7 different types of food: avocado, blueberry, potato, banana, spinach, pineapple, pumpkin
 1. the fan r&b is on the left of the person eating potato##1
 2. the fan classical is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
 3. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating banana##1
 4. the fan classical is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
 5. the person eating avocado is on the right of the fan trance##1
 6. the person eating banana is between the fan jazz and the person eating pineapple##2
 7. the fan trance is in the middle##1
 8. the person eating banana is on the left of the fan d&b##1
 9. the fan metal is the person eating blueberry##1
10. the person eating avocado is the fan r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Music-Genre      | jazz    | classical  | d&b  | trance  | r&b      | disco       | metal |
| Food   | spinach | banana | pineapple | pumpkin | avocado | potato | blueberry  |

