.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
There 7 different types of food: carrot, zucchini, spinach, papaya, avocado, onion, cucumber
There are 7 different favourite beverages: milk, coffee, mirinda, juice, hot-chocolate, water, almond-milk
1. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person eating zucchini##1
3. the person drinking milk is between the person eating cucumber and the person eating carrot##2
4. the person eating onion is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
5. the person drinking milk is in the middle##1
6. the person drinking water is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
7. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
8. the person drinking coffee is the person eating papaya##1
9. the person eating avocado is the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Food   | papaya      | avocado | carrot | spinach | cucumber      | zucchini      | onion |
| Beverage     | coffee | water | almond-milk       | milk | mirinda | hot-chocolate | juice |

