.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-8::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: train, taxi, airplane, scooter, quad-bike, helicopter, van
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: rowing, volleyball, handball, cycling, cricket, basketball, tennis
 1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
 4. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the van##1
 5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 6. the person driving the helicopter is between the person driving the scooter and the person driving the van##2
 7. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 8. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 9. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the train##1
10. the person driving the taxi is between the person driving the van and the person driving the train##2
11. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4     |         5          |     6      |     7     |
| Transport   | airplane  | quad-bike   | train         | taxi     | van              | helicopter    | scooter     |
| Sport        | basketball | volleyball | cricket | cycling | tennis | rowing | handball |

