.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-9::.
7 different games are played: snooker, canasta, chess, backgammon, go, monopoly, whist
House: cottage, palace, art-deco, gothic-revival, colonial, futuristic, tower
1. the person playing snooker is the futuristic house##1
2. the palace house is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
3. the person playing go is between the tower house and the colonial house##2
4. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
5. the cottage house is in the middle##1
6. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing chess##1
7. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the colonial house##1
8. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
9. the tower house is on the right of the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3    |    4    |    5     |     6     |   7    |
| Game   | canasta | backgammon     | monopoly | go | chess | whist  | snooker |
| House     | art-deco | gothic-revival | colonial   | cottage     | tower    | palace | futuristic   |

