.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-12::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: sudoku, traveling, woodworking, photography, collecting, rock-climbing, camping
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: march, june, july, april, november, january, may
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person who's birthday is in may##1
 2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is between the person who's hobby is photography and the person who's birthday is in march##2
 4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
 5. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left##1
10. the person who's birthday is in april is the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3   |   4   |    5    |   6    |   7    |
| Hobby   | photography | sudoku | traveling  | collecting   | rock-climbing | camping | woodworking |
| Birthday   | april     | may       | march | july | january  | june   | november   |

