 3. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person playing whist and the person who's birthday is in september##2
 4. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person who's birthday is in september##2
 5. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 7. the person playing poker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 8. the person playing domino is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 9. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
10. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1

